dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Vilas_Addresses_2017.gdb'. [Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://maps.vilascountywi.gov/data.htmlThis data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
